CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1961, pg. A6 reads: "Welcome Address - Andrew M. Bradley, Secretary of Property and Supplies of Pennsylvania, gave the welcome address, in behalf of Governor Lawrence, during the Grand Lodge session in the Steel City."
TitMainTitle: Andrew M. Bradley wearing dinner jacket and bow tie, giving welcome address during the Prince Hall Grand Lodge banquet in the Penn Sheraton hotel
